nodes.text: Gwendoline Yeo (born July 10, 1977) is a Singaporean-born American actress who provides the voice of Hologram VJ, Nala Se, Peppi Bow, Cato Parasitti, and Kalifa in Star Wars: The Clone Wars. She would later reprise her role as Nala Se in  Star Wars: The Bad Batch.
